<item>
  <title>Starting a notes section</title>
  <link>https://n-pearl.github.io/notes/welcome.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p>I’m going to be using this space to write up things as I learn them. Hopefully that forces me to actually understand a method well enough to explain it, and it leaves a trail of what I’ve been working through.</p>
<p>One thing I’ve enjoyed learning at the start of BUDS is the importance of effective visualizations. We’ve been leaning a lot on Claus O. Wilke’s <em>Fundamentals of Data Visualization</em> and, as he outlines, I’m trying my best to balance the art and science of it. Here’s a few examples I find cool!</p>
<p>A very basic ggplot method to view MPG by the number of Cylinders:</p>
<div class="cell">
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode cell-code" id="cb1" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode r code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb1-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">library</span>(tidyverse)</span></code></pre></div></div>
</div>
<div class="cell">
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode cell-code" id="cb2" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode r code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb2-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">ggplot</span>(mtcars, <span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">aes</span>(<span class="at" style="color: #657422;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">x =</span> <span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">factor</span>(cyl), <span class="at" style="color: #657422;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">y =</span> mpg)) <span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">+</span></span>
<span id="cb2-2">  <span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">geom_boxplot</span>()</span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="cell-output-display">
<div>
<figure class="figure">
<p><img src="https://n-pearl.github.io/notes/welcome_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png" class="img-fluid figure-img" width="672"></p>
</figure>
</div>
</div>
</div>
